{"id": 1177, "genre": 1001, "title": "发生了什么小事会让你觉得整趟旅行都被毁掉了？", "description": "天不时地不利人不和，酒店的wifi连不上……我的心情晴转多云。（题图来自：Sergiy Maidukov）", "record_count": 4844, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20160822104744kz9tMnPdQyga1rIW.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2016-08-23T03:00:23Z", "options": [{"id": 110080, "content": "水土不服", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 707545}, {"id": 111360, "content": "旅馆房间臭", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 732905}, {"id": 110081, "content": "当地人没有信用 手机没电没有网 攻略做的不对", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 724573}, {"id": 110082, "content": "队友什么都舍不得花钱体验", "image": null, "praise_count": 49, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 428367}, {"id": 110083, "content": "坐两天一夜的车结果只看到半天的景就爬不动了……然后又坐两天一夜的车返回", "image": null, "praise_count": 14, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 722677}, {"id": 110084, "content": "热???", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 303383}, {"id": 110085, "content": "酒店有蟑螂", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 728660}, {"id": 110086, "content": "没赶上飞机or火车", "image": null, "praise_count": 13, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 728664}, {"id": 110087, "content": "爱人带我去了他之前带他挚爱来的地方并且讲述着他们在这里的种种经历。", "image": null, "praise_count": 15, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 728665}, {"id": 127239, "content": "下大雨", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 807482}, {"id": 110088, "content": "没有热水", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 728666}, {"id": 110600, "content": "分享给好友却冷淡回应", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 732024}, {"id": 110089, "content": "航班延误", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 718222}, {"id": 110090, "content": "与旅伴意见不合", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 728692}, {"id": 110091, "content": "同伴和自己经常意见不符且一意孤行", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 100070}, {"id": 110092, "content": "没炮打", "image": null, "praise_count": 23, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 726678}, {"id": 110093, "content": "就算和男票头天晚上吵架了，第二天还是超高兴的到处耍哈哈哈哈只要有耍的吵架也可以放到回国再说完全不影响心情", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 589135}, {"id": 110094, "content": "人太多，一些人不太Nice", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 715245}, {"id": 110095, "content": "身边有个什么都爱抱怨的女同学?", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 686068}, {"id": 110096, "content": "旅伴都是王子和公主", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 532214}, {"id": 110608, "content": "天气不好", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 732098}, {"id": 110097, "content": "跟别人一起去，自己的意见不被看重", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 728713}, {"id": 110098, "content": "行李太重，却要每天换个旅馆", "image": null, "praise_count": 11, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 728713}, {"id": 110099, "content": "鼻炎+皮炎", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 609486}, {"id": 110104, "content": "目的地跟想象中完全不同", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 465613}, {"id": 110105, "content": "大姨妈来了", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 600260}, {"id": 112153, "content": "在一个网络不稳定的酒店用微信告诉你她出去了卡给了另一个旅伴", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 741508}, {"id": 135194, "content": "跟同伴产生分歧。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 839386}, {"id": 110106, "content": "花心思定的酒店没有预想的好！！！", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 718424}, {"id": 110107, "content": "分手", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 692601}, {"id": 110108, "content": "一旦和想象不同\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 623377}, {"id": 110620, "content": "其实旅途中的一切都是值得，哪怕是遇到一些不想遇到的。", "image": "img/option/option/20160825174752XINYlDyr7jzuP8F5", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 732127}, {"id": 110109, "content": "其他人不积极出钱", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 728744}, {"id": 110110, "content": "和同行的人闹别扭", "image": null, "praise_count": 12, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 684069}, {"id": 110111, "content": "本来要逃离的家人的烦心事", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 659288}, {"id": 110112, "content": "跟现任一起在外国遇到ex……", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 130117}, {"id": 110113, "content": "早早就做好旅行计划，到达目地地后却兴趣全无", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 728390}, {"id": 110114, "content": "余额不足", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 425089}, {"id": 110115, "content": "被跟团，然后被骗", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 728754}, {"id": 110116, "content": "便秘…", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 728760}, {"id": 110117, "content": "同行的全程玩手机", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 728773}, {"id": 110118, "content": "大量行李 + 没有车", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 581136}, {"id": 110119, "content": "忘带或者带差洗漱用品", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 667385}, {"id": 110375, "content": "一个人", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 730304}, {"id": 113447, "content": "出行几人，所有人都指望你一个人安排全程事情", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 747023}, {"id": 121639, "content": "赶时间……", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 783564}, {"id": 110120, "content": "手机/相机被偷，顿时任何玩的心情都没了。", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 139557}, {"id": 110121, "content": "生病", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 475546}, {"id": 110122, "content": "丢手机！", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 723046}, {"id": 110123, "content": "d", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 473557}]}